cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CL

The paper proposes a novel boosting approach for multi-class classification problems using random projections. This approach is evaluated on synthetic, machine learning, and visual recognition datasets, indicating that it is relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on machine learning and classification, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
